<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bang-n">bang <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bæŋ/    美 /bæŋ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>砰的一声：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The firework exploded <strong>with a</strong> loud <strong>bang</strong>. 
烟火砰的一声爆开了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>猛击；猛撞：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He gave the drum a bang. 
他用力敲了一下鼓。</p></div></div>